long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Celeb Trends is an extension that lets you bring beautiful themed images to your everyday devices. The Celeb Trends aims to provide exclusive and comprehensive information about fashion, beauty and culture.

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I agree to the installation. and accept the Celeb Trends extension and configure the Chrome New Tab search engine on Microsoft Bing as described in the terms of service: http://www.kayjag.com/info/privacy
